{"kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/gettingstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/GettingStarted","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This guide walks through the four steps to integrate "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":" into a Swidux app: add the package, configure RevenueCat, register the plugin, and attach the UI. It is the shortest path from a wired Swidux app to a working paywall. For deeper coverage of any step, follow the linked how-tos."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This package assumes you already use Swidux. If you don’t, work through Swidux’s own getting-started guide first."}]},{"anchor":"Add-the-Package","type":"heading","text":"Add the Package","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode:"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" File > Add Package Dependencies, paste "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"https:\/\/github.com\/HeirloomLogic\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":". Add the products you need:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":" — the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation and mock."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"},{"type":"text","text":" — adds the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatCustomerCenter"},{"type":"text","text":" view modifiers (depends on RevenueCatUI)."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Package.swift:"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"code":[".package(url: \"https:\/\/github.com\/HeirloomLogic\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\", from: \"1.0.0\"),"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"code":[".product(name: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\", package: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\"),",".product(name: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI\", package: \"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\"),"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Configure-the-paywall-at-launch","type":"heading","text":"Configure the paywall at launch","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" calls into "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.shared"},{"type":"text","text":" under the hood. Configure the paywall before constructing the store:"}]},{"code":["\/\/ MyApp.swift","import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","import SwiftUI","","@main","struct MyApp: App {","    @State private var store: AppStore","","    init() {","        RevenueCatPaywall.configure(apiKey: \"your_revenuecat_api_key\")","        _store = State(wrappedValue: AppStore.configured())","    }","","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup { ContentView().environment(store) }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pass "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"appUserID"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userDefaults"},{"type":"text","text":" (for app-group sharing with widgets), "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"logLevel"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"entitlementVerification"},{"type":"text","text":" (signed entitlement verification), or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"purchasesAreCompletedBy"},{"type":"text","text":"\/"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"storeKitVersion"},{"type":"text","text":" (app-completed purchases) if you need them — see "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywall\/configure(apiKey:appUserID:userDefaults:logLevel:entitlementVerification:purchasesAreCompletedBy:storeKitVersion:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"anchor":"Register-the-paywall-plugin","type":"heading","text":"Register the paywall plugin","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pass "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallPlugin"},{"type":"text","text":" in your "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Store.configured()"},{"type":"text","text":" factory:"}]},{"code":["import Swidux","import SwiduxPaywall","import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","","extension Store where State == AppState, Action == AppAction {","    static func configured() -> AppStore {","        let plugins = PluginHost<AppState, AppAction>()","","        plugins.register(","            PaywallPlugin<AppState, AppAction>(","                state: \\.paywall,","                action: AppAction.paywall,","                extractAction: { if case .paywall(let a) = $0 { return a }; return nil },","                service: ResilientPaywallService(","                    base: RevenueCatPaywallService(entitlementID: \"pro\"),","                    store: UserDefaultsKeyValueStore()","                )","            )","        )","","        return Store(","            initialState: AppState(),","            reducer: AppReducer().reduce,","            plugins: plugins","        )","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResilientPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" (from SwiduxPaywall) persists the last entitlement snapshot a successful read delivered. Without it, a slow or failing network at cold launch leaves "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallState"},{"type":"text","text":" at its free default and gates paying users out of their features until the first successful read; with it, the last-known-good state holds until live data arrives, and the server stays authoritative — a genuine lapse is honoured on the next successful read. Wrap the RevenueCat service in it for production."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Start the entitlement stream on the root view so the gate reflects RevenueCat’s state from launch:"}]},{"code":["struct ContentView: View {","    @Environment(AppStore.self) private var store","","    var body: some View {","        RootContent()","            .task { store.send(.paywall(.observeCustomerInfo)) }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Gate features by reading "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"store.paywall.isGateSatisfied"},{"type":"text","text":". See "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for the full plugin lifecycle."}]},{"anchor":"Attach-the-UI","type":"heading","text":"Attach the UI","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Attach the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"revenueCatPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to a root view, driven by paywall state:"}]},{"code":["import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","","struct RootView: View {","    @Environment(AppStore.self) private var store","","    var body: some View {","        ContentView()","            .revenueCatPaywall(state: store.paywall) { action in","                store.send(.paywall(action))","            }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Trigger the paywall from a gated feature with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".paywall(.request(reason:))"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"code":["Button(\"Export PDF\") {","    if store.paywall.isGateSatisfied {","        store.send(.export(.exportPDF))","    } else {","        store.send(.paywall(.request(reason: \"export-pdf\")))","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for manual wiring with the primitive modifiers, customer-center triggering, and dismiss semantics."}]},{"anchor":"Next-Steps","type":"heading","text":"Next Steps","level":2},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"},{"type":"text","text":" — Detailed walkthrough of the service lifecycle and error handling."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToAddAPermanentLicense"},{"type":"text","text":" — Add a lifetime entitlement alongside the subscription."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPreviewAndTest"},{"type":"text","text":" — Drive entitlement state from previews and tests."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI"},{"type":"text","text":" — Wire the bundled view modifiers."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/PlatformBehavior"},{"type":"text","text":" — Why iOS and macOS behave differently."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping"},{"type":"text","text":" — How RevenueCat entitlements map to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EntitlementSnapshot"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Add the package, configure RevenueCat, register the paywall plugin, and present the bundled sheets."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"]]},"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Getting Started with SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},"references":{"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/RevenueCatPaywall/configure(apiKey:appUserID:userDefaults:logLevel:entitlementVerification:purchasesAreCompletedBy:storeKitVersion:)":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/RevenueCatPaywall\/configure(apiKey:appUserID:userDefaults:logLevel:entitlementVerification:purchasesAreCompletedBy:storeKitVersion:)","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/revenuecatpaywall\/configure(apikey:appuserid:userdefaults:loglevel:entitlementverification:purchasesarecompletedby:storekitversion:)","fragments":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"configure","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"apiKey","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"appUserID","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":"?